Absolutely pouring, had/forced to leave the park at 830 due to severe flash flooding. Ended up birding the roads around the park (included in this list). Kinda got extorted. Entrance fee is criminal. For 6 hours, ended up paying almost as much as I did for 12 hours in Yala with brekkie and lunch included. So it goes. Absolutely pouring, had/forced to leave the park at 830 due to severe flash flooding. Ended up birding the roads around the park (included in this list). Non avian highlight was a rouge elephant that tried to run the car off the road.--I honestly cant believe I had such a high species total given the rain (and frankly my low effort). I didnt think I wouldve broke 60 until I started making the checklist. I imagine that on a nicer day with more of a concerted effort towards passerines, 120 would be quite possible in a morning.

TRIP COMMENTS: Kinda got extorted. Entrance fee is criminal. For 6 hours, ended up paying almost as much as I did for 12 hours in Yala with brekkie and lunch included. So it goes. Absolutely pouring, had/forced to leave the park at 830 due to severe flash flooding. Ended up birding the roads around the park (included in this list). Non avian highlight was a rouge elephant that tried to run the car off the road.--I honestly cant believe I had such a high species total given the rain (and frankly my low effort).
